descriptionHtml:
Original Mod and Instructions Provided Here:
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30568/

This is Simply a Replacer for a Already Existing Mod that will add Morrowind and Oblivions to the Game.
As Some People have Requested, If the Original Mod Author Would like to include my version as a Variant he has that right.
What this File Does is Remove all but the Oblivion and Morrowind Tracks from the Game Barring the Boss/Special Tracks Which have been left intact.
